config TEST_ASYNC_DRIVER_PROBE
	tristate "Build kernel module to test asynchronous driver probing"
	depends on m
	help
	  Enabling this option produces a kernel module that allows
	  testing asynchronous driver probing by the device core.
	  The module name will be test_async_driver_probe.ko

	  If unsure say N.

config TEST_ASYNC_FW_LOAD
	tristate "Build kernel module to test asynchronous firmware loading"
	depends on m
	help
	  Enabling this options produces a kernel module that can test
	  asynchronous firmware loading by the device core. The module name
	  will be test_async_fw_load.ko.

	  If unsure say N.
